com.wingfoot.wsdl
Class WSDLHolder

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.wingfoot.wsdl.WSDLHolder
All Implemented Interfaces:
XMLHolder
public class WSDLHolder
extends java.lang.Object
implements XMLHolder

Encapsulates a well formed WSDL.

A WSDL has many components. The getXXX and setXXX methods allow for addition of components from the WSDL.

getNormalizedModelGroupDefinition

public ModelGroupDefinition getNormalizedModelGroupDefinition(ModelGroupDefinition mgd)
Given a ModelGroupDefinition (a Component) that is a reference to another to another ModelGroupDefinition, retrieves the ModelGroupDefinition that is being referred to.

If the mgd is not a reference then mgd is returned back.

If mgd is null or if the reference to the element is not present in this SchemaHolder, null is returned.

If the referenced ModelGroupDefinition is present in this SchemaHolder then the referenced ModelGroupDefinition is returned.

Parameters:
mgd - ModelGroupDefinition that has a ref attribute in it.
Returns:
ModelGroupDefinition the referenced ModelGroupDefinition.
